column5: Alphonze omfg hahhhahhaahaha so fucking cute

My mom was the most generous and emotionally supportive mom ever when she was sober, I adored her .
When she wasn’t sober I was tormented with her black outs, being called names , kicked out and my stuff ruined and thrown out.
She’s passed now

My Aries moon is very strong lol. When I need something I need it now and all that maters is someone tends to my emotional well being until I feel okay again.
I love this. Very well done

It’s my birthday tomorrow. 
Does anyone know what this could possibly mean for me? :/

“I learned that love is dead and people just get fucked instead. All the while making friends, just to fuck them in the end” - dystopia 

PS thank you for posting this. I thought I was fucked for being that way, so it’s nice to know that I’m not alone.
